      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Snowpack thickness varies depending on exposure and altitude; especially on shady slopes, eroded areas are interspersed with deposits. In many places, hard surface crusts are present, and near the ridges, there are evident cornices. Weak layers exist in the snowpack in particular on shady slopes. The weather conditions will give rise to gradual and thorough wetting of the snowpack."
